{"blocks":[{"key":"716nm","text":"For regular CRISPR/Cas9 editing, use:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":12,"length":20}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"63k5m","text":"    5 µl, autoclaved H2O","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5ah11","text":"    2 µl, 40 µM purified Cas9 protein","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f58er","text":"    3 µl, 100 µM synthetic sgRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ub0g","text":"For prime editing PE2 strategy, use:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":18,"length":12}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6cdko","text":"    7-x µl, autoclaved H2O","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3ril8","text":"    x µl (90 pmol), purified PE2 protein","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"13mis","text":"    3 µl, 100 µM synthetic pegRNA","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"16v1u","text":"Pipet the proper amount of each component in the order showing above into a microcentrifuge tube. Mix using a P10/20 tip. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
